<section id="block-block-2" class="block block-block header-slogan clearfix">

      
   <p>We are a leading UK charity which raises money to fund research into the causes of eye disease, the development of treatments and the&nbsp;prevention of blindness.</p>
 
</section> <!-- /.block -->
